The program is written in Python
The program runs on a raspberry pi CM4
This is a controller for a two wheel balancing robot.
The drive controller is embedded and accessed through xgo-toolkit.
The xgo-toolkit is located at ~/xgo-toolkit.
Any files created for testing purposes should begin with 'test_'
All program files should be in the app folder
For context, there is a copy of the client code at /home/pi/Rider-PC-Client, this is not to be modified.